INSERT INTO frecency_aggregates (
                    entity_id,
                    entity_type,
                    user_id,
                    event_count,
                    frecency_score,
                    first_event,
                    recent_events
                )
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
                ON CONFLICT (user_id, entity_type, entity_id)
                DO UPDATE SET
                    event_count = EXCLUDED.event_count,
                    frecency_score = EXCLUDED.frecency_score,
                    recent_events = EXCLUDED.recent_events
